2f6","tid":2298424,"uid":126590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c9d423ca10cff1626b59a2bfa1e5d65a1ce87d9f","tid":2298424,"uid":238214,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"686b0dd3d78b685dea0724c3f23e6a9404eab3b0","tid":2298424,"uid":77968,"like":122,"dislike":0,"score":122,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:43:19.000Z","msg":"咩強制安心出行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲阿伯阿婆都唔識用智能手機，你叫佢掃QR code ，佢屌你老母就有"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T01:33:29.000Z","msg":"好多都識用 唔好諗到長者係廢柴至得架<br />\n大把長者會學新野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"識用手機send Whatsapp 就當係識新科技咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教人用zoom教咗兩日都仲要傍住佢開工呀<br />\n我同佢前日一齊學架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"【612Reminder淺談瘟疫政治：不安出行App】<br />\n<br />\n無好氣講廢話。簡單黎講，如果大家覺得耍小聰明就對付到呢個港版健康碼嘅話，開定一二一二追悼會都得。<br />\n<br />\n根據科學園職員 消息，科學園等地即將強制任何人進出前必須嘟不安出行QR code。如果唔配合，接待員、保安唔俾你入去。<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，政府已經 *推動緊* 強制全民download不安出行，港版健康碼正式殺到埋身。<br />\n<br />\n可能會有人問：傻的嗎？老餅鬼識用App。<br />\n明報社評已經幫你諗埋：豁免特定年齡群組人士咪得。<br />\n<br />\n反正政府本意就係搞個數據煉獄針對監視後生黃絲，唔洗周圍哭喪問點解政府唔用Apple同Google嘅疫情追蹤系統，要用納稅人錢搞個偽加密app。 <br />\n<br />\n上網所謂嘅「短期解決方法」近乎無用：<br />\n1. 用鬼機鬼卡<br />\n-&gt; 強制實名制就track到你，最多叫攞唔到你主機啲data，除非你覺得港版健康碼自身無問題。<br />\n2. 收集曬全部地方嘅QR code，一個鐘掃12個地方吹咩？<br />\n-&gt; 求其一個地方奶嘢就要被逼自我隔離，自己玩自己。Check到玩嘢分分鐘要比狗咬。<br />\n3. 用偽出行App呃實Q<br />\n-&gt; 唔知實名制後政府dept見到一個人長期無Check in/out record會點諗。（所以唔想無啦啦比狗搞嘅話，都係要定期打卡。）<br />\n<br />\n心水清少少都知淨係靠打文宣戰係阻唔到任何濕鳩政策，599G如是，國安法亦如是。<br />\n好聽叫文宣戰，難聽叫口交部。<br />\n無意用實際行動反抗嘅話，大家自求多福啦。<br />\n人面識別、智慧監獄、健康碼，陸續有黎。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n1. 科學園交通苦主聯盟Facebook<br />\n (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkstptraffic/photos/a.1634068003539782/2789705471309357/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkstptraffic%2Fphotos%2Fa.1634068003539782%2F2789705471309357%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=511a897d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkstptraffic/photos/a.1634068003539782/2789705471309357/</a>)2. 明報社評：「安心出行」成習慣 適度強制不可免<br />\n (<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%A4%BE%E8%A9%95/article/20201125/s00003/1606241951618/%E7%A4%BE%E8%A9%95-%E3%80%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8D%E6%88%90%E7%BF%92%E6%85%A3-%E9%81%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%85%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25A9%2595%2Farticle%2F20201125%2Fs00003%2F1606241951618%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25A9%2595-%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25BF%2592%25E6%2585%25A3-%25E9%2581%25A9%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%2585%258D&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=33b87996\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25A9%2595%2Farticle%2F20201125%2Fs00003%2F1606241951618%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25A9%2595-%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25BF%2592%25E6%2585%25A3-%25E9%2581%25A9%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%2585%258D&h=b19f7080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%A4%BE%E8%A9%95/article/20201125/s00003/1606241951618/%E7%A4%BE%E8%A9%95-%E3%80%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8D%E6%88%90%E7%BF%92%E6%85%A3-%E9%81%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%85%8D</a>)3. HeaDuck研究所：「安心出行」能否安心使用？<br />\n<br />\n#Reminder隨筆 (<a href=\"http://blog.headuck.com/2020/11/19/%E3%80%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9F%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F